    • Field Detail

      • security

        public APSSecurityLevel security
        security level of this APS. NONE : APS not encrypted, records not encrypted MEDIUM : APS is encrypted and all containing records are encrypted with the APS key HIGH : APS is encrypted and each record is encrypted with its own key

      • version

        public long version
        timestamp of last change

      • keys

        public java.util.Map<java.lang.String,byte[]> keys
        key table. one entry for each entity that has access to this APS. map keys are the object ids of the entities and the word "owner" for the owner of the APS. each map value is the RSA encrypted AES key of this APS.

      • encrypted

        public byte[] encrypted
        the encrypted body of this APS

      • permissions

        the unencrypted body of this APS.

      • unmerged

        public java.util.List<AccessPermissionSet> unmerged
        additional blocks of data for this APS that need to be merged into this part (the main part)
